---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="referrer" content="no-referrer" />
  <title>Support a Cause — Caribbean Countdowns</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      background: #0f0f0f;
      color: #e0e0e0;
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    .page { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 48px 24px 80px; }

    .header-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .site-title {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.3px;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .back-link {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #555;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .back-link:hover { color: #999; }

    .lang-group {
      display: flex;
      gap: 4px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .lang-btn {
      background: transparent;
      border: 1px solid #555;
      border-radius: 3px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      color: #aaa;
      font-family: inherit;
      transition: all 0.15s;
    }
    .lang-btn:hover { border-color: #888; color: #eee; }
    .lang-btn.active { background: #1e3a5f; border-color: #2d6aa0; color: #7ec8e3; }

    .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid #2e2e2e; margin: 32px 0; }

    h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    p { color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 12px; }

    .steps {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }

    .step {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .step-num {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #1e3a5f;
      border: 1px solid #2d6aa0;
      color: #7ec8e3;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .step-body strong {
      display: block;
      color: #eee;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .step-body span { color: #888; font-size: 12px; }

    .ngo-card {
      background: #111;
      border: 1px solid #2e2e2e;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .ngo-badge {
      background: #0d2a2a;
      border: 1px solid #065f46;
      color: #34d399;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 2px 8px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      white-space: nowrap;
      margin-top: 3px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .ngo-info strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .ngo-info p { color: #888; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 8px; }

    .ngo-link {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #7ec8e3;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .ngo-link:hover { color: #b3e0f2; }

    .tiers {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }

    .tier {
      background: #111;
      border: 1px solid #2e2e2e;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .tier-name {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #7ec8e3;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .tier-amount {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .tier-amount span {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #555;
    }

    .tier ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .tier ul li {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
      padding: 3px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid #1e1e1e;
    }

    .tier ul li:first-child { border-top: none; }

    .cta-block {
      background: #111;
      border: 1px solid #2e2e2e;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 8px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .cta-block p { margin: 0; color: #888; font-size: 13px; }

    .cta-btn {
      background: #1e3a5f;
      border: 1px solid #2d6aa0;
      color: #7ec8e3;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      padding: 8px 20px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-decoration: none;
      white-space: nowrap;
      transition: background 0.15s;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .cta-btn:hover { background: #254e7a; text-decoration: none; color: #b3e0f2; }

    .current-sponsors {
      margin-top: 8px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .sponsor-card {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 20px;
      background: #111;
      border: 1px solid #2e2e2e;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color 0.15s;
    }
    .sponsor-card:hover { border-color: #444; text-decoration: none; }

    .sponsor-logo {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .sponsor-logo img { height: 36px; display: block; }

    .sponsor-info strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #eee;
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }
    .sponsor-info p { font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin: 0; }

    .sponsor-tier-badge {
      margin-left: auto;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 2px 8px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      background: #1e3a5f;
      color: #7ec8e3;
      border: 1px solid #2d6aa0;
      white-space: nowrap;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .sponsor-slot-empty {
      border: 1px dashed #2e2e2e;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 28px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #333;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="page">

    <div class="header-row">
      <h1 class="site-title">
        <a href="/" style="color:inherit;">Caribbean Countdowns</a>
      </h1>
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;">
        <a class="back-link" href="/">
          <span class="t-en">← Back</span>
          <span class="t-fr">← Retour</span>
          <span class="t-kr">← Retounen</span>
          <span class="t-es">← Volver</span>
        </a>
        <div class="lang-group">
          <button class="lang-btn" data-lang="en" onclick="setLang('en')">EN</button>
          <button class="lang-btn" data-lang="fr" onclick="setLang('fr')">FR</button>
          <button class="lang-btn" data-lang="kr" onclick="setLang('kr')">KR</button>
          <button class="lang-btn" data-lang="es" onclick="setLang('es')">ES</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider" />

    <!-- Intro -->
    <h2>
      <span class="t-en">Support a cause, get visibility</span>
      <span class="t-fr">Soutenez une cause, gagnez en visibilité</span>
      <span class="t-kr">Sipòté on koz, jwenn vizibilité</span>
      <span class="t-es">Apoya una causa, gana visibilidad</span>
    </h2>

    <p>
      <span class="t-en">Caribbean Countdowns offers visibility to brands and organizations that support causes protecting the Caribbean. No money goes to this site — 100% of donations go directly to the featured NGO.</span>
      <span class="t-fr">Caribbean Countdowns offre de la visibilité aux marques et organisations qui soutiennent des causes protégeant la Caraïbe. Aucun argent ne va à ce site — 100 % des dons vont directement à l'ONG partenaire.</span>
      <span class="t-kr">Caribbean Countdowns ofri vizibilité bay mak épi òganizasyon ki sipòté koz pou pwotéjé Karayib la. Okenn lajan pa alé nan sit la — 100% don alé dirèktèman bay NGO patnè a.</span>
      <span class="t-es">Caribbean Countdowns ofrece visibilidad a marcas y organizaciones que apoyan causas que protegen el Caribe. Ningún dinero va a este sitio — el 100% de las donaciones van directamente a la ONG destacada.</span>
    </p>

    <hr class="divider" />

    <!-- How it works -->
    <h2>
      <span class="t-en">How it works</span>
      <span class="t-fr">Comment ça fonctionne</span>
      <span class="t-kr">Kouman sa mache</span>
      <span class="t-es">Cómo funciona</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <strong>
            <span class="t-en">Choose a tier and donate</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Choisissez un palier et faites un don</span>
            <span class="t-kr">Chwazi on nivo épi fè on don</span>
            <span class="t-es">Elige un nivel y dona</span>
          </strong>
          <span>
            <span class="t-en">Make your donation directly to the featured NGO. Keep your proof of donation.</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Faites votre don directement à l'ONG partenaire. Gardez votre preuve de don.</span>
            <span class="t-kr">Fè don ou dirèktèman bay NGO a. Gadé prèv don ou.</span>
            <span class="t-es">Haz tu donación directamente a la ONG destacada. Guarda tu comprobante.</span>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <strong>
            <span class="t-en">Send us your donation receipt + your website link or logo</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Envoyez-nous votre reçu de don + le lien de votre site ou logo</span>
            <span class="t-kr">Voye nou resi don ou + lyen sit ou a oswa logo a</span>
            <span class="t-es">Envíanos tu comprobante de donación + el enlace de tu sitio web o logo</span>
          </strong>
          <span>
            <span class="t-en">We will verify directly with them to prevent fraud. Your identity will not be shared with them unless you request it.</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Nous vérifierons directement auprès d'eux pour éviter les faux reçus. Votre identité ne leur sera pas transmise sauf si vous le souhaitez.</span>
            <span class="t-kr">Nou ké vérifié dirèktèman avèk yo pou évité fo resi. Yo pa ké konnen non ou si ou pa vlé sa.</span>
            <span class="t-es">Verificaremos directamente con ellos para evitar fraudes. Tu identidad no será compartida salvo que lo solicites.</span>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <strong>
            <span class="t-en">You will appears on the site</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Vous apparaitrez sur le site</span>
            <span class="t-kr">Ou ké parèt sou sit la</span>
            <span class="t-es">Tu aparece en el sitio</span>
          </strong>
          <span>
            <span class="t-en">Your brand or organization is listed on the main page for the duration of your tier.</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Votre marque ou organisation est affichée sur la page principale pendant la durée de votre palier.</span>
            <span class="t-kr">Mak ou, òganizasyon ou afiche sou paj prensipal la pandan diré nivo ou a.</span>
            <span class="t-es">Tu marca u organización aparece en la página principal durante el periodo de tu nivel.</span>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider" />

    <!-- Featured NGO -->
    <h2>
      <span class="t-en">Current cause</span>
      <span class="t-fr">Cause actuelle</span>
      <span class="t-kr">Koz aktyèl la</span>
      <span class="t-es">Causa actual</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="ngo-card">
      <span class="ngo-badge">NGO</span>
      <div class="ngo-info">
        <strong>L'Asso-Mer</strong>
        <p>
          <span class="t-en">Marine conservation nonprofit based in Martinique. Since 2016, they protect coral reefs, sea turtles and Caribbean marine heritage through science, restoration, and public education.</span>
          <span class="t-fr">Association de conservation marine basée en Martinique. Depuis 2016, ils protègent les récifs coralliens, les tortues marines et le patrimoine marin caribéen par la science, la restauration et la sensibilisation.</span>
          <span class="t-kr">Asosyasyon konsèvasyon maren sitié Matinik. Depi 2016, yo ka pwotéjé koray, tòti maren épi patrimwàn maren Karayib la atravè siyans, restòrasyon épi edikayon piblik.</span>
          <span class="t-es">ONG de conservación marina con sede en Martinica. Desde 2016 protegen los arrecifes de coral, las tortugas marinas y el patrimonio marino caribeño a través de la ciencia, la restauración y la educación.</span>
        </p>
        <a class="ngo-link" href="https://www.lassomer.fr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">lassomer.fr ↗</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-block" style="margin-top:0;">
      <p style="color:#ddd;">
        <span class="t-en">Are you an NGO or nonprofit protecting the Caribbean? Apply for a free listing.</span>
        <span class="t-fr">Vous êtes une ONG ou association protégeant la Caraïbe ? Demandez un référencement gratuit.</span>
        <span class="t-kr">Ou se yon ONG oswa asosyasyon ki pwotéjé Karayib la ? Mandé yon enskripsyon gratis.</span>
        <span class="t-es">¿Eres una ONG o asociación que protege el Caribe? Solicita un listado gratuito.</span>
      </p>
      <a class="cta-btn" href="mailto:admin.hxqxk@silomails.com?subject=NGO%20listing%20request%20—%20Caribbean%20Countdowns">
        <span class="t-en">Contact us</span>
        <span class="t-fr">Nous contacter</span>
        <span class="t-kr">Kontakte nou</span>
        <span class="t-es">Contáctanos</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider" />

    <!-- Tiers -->
    <h2>
      <span class="t-en">Sponsorship tiers</span>
      <span class="t-fr">Paliers de sponsoring</span>
      <span class="t-kr">Nivo parenaj</span>
      <span class="t-es">Niveles de patrocinio</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="tiers">
      <div class="tier">
        <div class="tier-name">
          <span class="t-en">Friend</span>
          <span class="t-fr">Ami</span>
          <span class="t-kr">Zanmi</span>
          <span class="t-es">Amigo</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-amount">€50 <span>/ <span class="t-en">1 month of visibility</span><span class="t-fr">1 mois de visibilité</span><span class="t-kr">1 mwa vizibilité</span><span class="t-es">1 mes de visibilidad</span></span></div>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <span class="t-en">Name + link on main page</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Nom + lien sur la page principale</span>
            <span class="t-kr">Non + lyen sou paj prensipal</span>
            <span class="t-es">Nombre + enlace en página principal</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="t-en">Listed on this page</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Listé sur cette page</span>
            <span class="t-kr">Listé sou paj sa a</span>
            <span class="t-es">Listado en esta página</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="tier">
        <div class="tier-name">
          <span class="t-en">Supporter</span>
          <span class="t-fr">Soutien</span>
          <span class="t-kr">Sipòtè</span>
          <span class="t-es">Colaborador</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-amount">€150 <span>/ <span class="t-en">3 months of visibility</span><span class="t-fr">3 mois de visibilité</span><span class="t-kr">3 mwa vizibilité</span><span class="t-es">3 meses de visibilidad</span></span></div>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <span class="t-en">Name + link on main page</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Nom + lien sur la page principale</span>
            <span class="t-kr">Non + lyen sou paj prensipal</span>
            <span class="t-es">Nombre + enlace en página principal</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="t-en">Logo displayed</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Logo affiché</span>
            <span class="t-kr">Logo afichè</span>
            <span class="t-es">Logo visible</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="t-en">Listed on this page</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Listé sur cette page</span>
            <span class="t-kr">Listé sou paj sa a</span>
            <span class="t-es">Listado en esta página</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="tier">
        <div class="tier-name">
          <span class="t-en">Partner</span>
          <span class="t-fr">Partenaire</span>
          <span class="t-kr">Patnè</span>
          <span class="t-es">Socio</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-amount">€400 <span>/ <span class="t-en">6 months of visibility</span><span class="t-fr">6 mois de visibilité</span><span class="t-kr">6 mwa vizibilité</span><span class="t-es">6 meses de visibilidad</span></span></div>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <span class="t-en">Name + link on main page</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Nom + lien sur la page principale</span>
            <span class="t-kr">Non + lyen sou paj prensipal</span>
            <span class="t-es">Nombre + enlace en página principal</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="t-en">Logo displayed (prominent)</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Logo affiché (en évidence)</span>
            <span class="t-kr">Logo afichè (an evid)</span>
            <span class="t-es">Logo visible (destacado)</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="t-en">Listed on this page</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Listé sur cette page</span>
            <span class="t-kr">Listé sou paj sa a</span>
            <span class="t-es">Listado en esta página</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="t-en">Short description included</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Courte description incluse</span>
            <span class="t-kr">Ti deskripsyon enkli</span>
            <span class="t-es">Breve descripción incluida</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="cta-block">
      <p>
        <span class="t-en">Interested? Email us with your donation receipt and your details.</span>
        <span class="t-fr">Intéressé·e ? Écrivez-nous avec votre reçu de don et vos informations.</span>
        <span class="t-kr">Entéresé ? Ekri nou avèk resi don ou épi enfòmasyon ou yo.</span>
        <span class="t-es">¿Interesado? Escríbenos con tu comprobante de donación y tus datos.</span>
      </p>
      <a class="cta-btn" href="mailto:admin.hxqxk@silomails.com?subject=Sponsor%20Caribbean%20Countdowns">
        <span class="t-en">Contact us</span>
        <span class="t-fr">Nous contacter</span>
        <span class="t-kr">Kontakte nou</span>
        <span class="t-es">Contáctanos</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider" />

    <!-- Current sponsors -->
    <h2>
      <span class="t-en">Current sponsors</span>
      <span class="t-fr">Sponsors actuels</span>
      <span class="t-kr">Sponsors aktyèl yo</span>
      <span class="t-es">Patrocinadores actuales</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="current-sponsors">
      <a class="sponsor-card" href="https://lereveantillais.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <div class="sponsor-logo">
          <img src="/images/sponsors/lereve-antillais.jpg" alt="Le Rêve Antillais" />
        </div>
        <div class="sponsor-info">
          <strong>Le Rêve Antillais</strong>
          <p>
            <span class="t-en">Caribbean booking agency — connecting artists, producers and events across the Caribbean.</span>
            <span class="t-fr">Agence de booking caribéenne — connecter artistes, producteurs et événements à travers la Caraïbe.</span>
            <span class="t-kr">Ajans booking karayibèn — konèkté atis, pwodiktè épi évènman an Karayib la.</span>
            <span class="t-es">Agencia de booking caribeña — conectando artistas, productores y eventos en el Caribe.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <span class="sponsor-tier-badge">Partner</span>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <script src="/scripts/lang.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
